                description: 'Deployed Jenkins and Apache Tomcat inside a Minikube Kubernetes cluster for local orchestration practice. Manually copied the WAR artifact into the Tomcat pod and exposed the application externally through a NodePort service. Validated browser access to the deployed Java web application and practiced core Kubernetes deployment workflows.',
